You will create and process the appropriate documents to complete the sales order and record the lot number. You will use quick processing to illustrated expedited processing of the sales order. ==Configuration Overview== In the ''U100'' data set, the ''Inventory'' feature in the ''Inventory and Order Management'' group of features has been enabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] ([~/?ScreenId=CS100000|CS100000]) form.{br}
